    "longBusinessSummary": "Thuan An Wood Processing Joint Stock Company primarily engages in the production and sale of wooden furniture primarily in Vietnam and internationally. The company offers house and outdoor products, including dining tables and chairs, dressing tables and drawers, beds, sideboards, high-boards, bedside tables, tallboys, nightstands, wardrobes, media consoles and towers, media desks, dressers, shelves and shelving units, cabinets, lounge chairs, and office meeting tables. It also provides various services, including civil engineering, housing construction, and installation of wooden furniture, as well as construction of technical works and industrial projects. In addition, the company is involved in buying and selling beds, wardrobes, tables, and chairs, as well as latex rubber and wood products; real estate business; wholesale of other household appliances; and trading industrial, mining, forestry, and construction equipment. It exports its products to Indonesia, Malaysia, Thailand, Europe, and the United States. The company was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Thuan An, Vietnam.",
